The LORD reigns, let the earth rejoice; Let the many islands be glad. -- psalms 97:1
.
Clouds and thick darkness surround Him; Righteousness and justice are the foundation of His throne. -- psalms 97:2
.
Fire goes before Him And burns up His adversaries round about. -- psalms 97:3
.
His lightnings lit up the world; The earth saw and trembled. -- psalms 97:4
.
The mountains melted like wax at the presence of the LORD, At the presence of the Lord of the whole earth. -- psalms 97:5
.
The heavens declare His righteousness, And all the peoples have seen His glory. -- psalms 97:6
.
