.
If You, LORD, should mark iniquities, O Lord, who could stand? -- psalms 130:3
.
But there is forgiveness with You, That You may be feared. -- psalms 130:4
.
I wait for the LORD, my soul does wait, And in His word do I hope. -- psalms 130:5
.
My soul waits for the Lord More than the watchmen for the morning; Indeed, more than the watchmen for the morning. -- psalms 130:6
.
